  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><a href="images/crusader/crushand.jpg"><img src="images/crusader/small/crushand_small1.jpg" border=0 alt width="100" height="75" align="right"></a>For situations needing dexterity, or at the pilots
    wish, the Crusader's left arm can instead be fitted with a powered hand.</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>
      <hr>
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><a href="images/crusader/cruscannon.jpg"><img src="images/crusader/small/cruscannon_small1.jpg" border=0 alt width="100" height="75" align="right"></a>Rounding out the Crusader's arsenal is the Pulse
    Rifle found on the Marauder. Employing the adage &quot;if it ain't broke, don't fix
    it,&quot; Triton has chosen to continue the use of this weapon due to it's ease of use and
      maintainence, durability, and it's excellent stopping power.</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>
